Description:
    Installs the search component including a search page example connected to a homepage. The
    homepage can be configured with the "---homepage_path" parameter.

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:search`
    `rails generate cms:component:search --homepage_path=/website/en`

    CMS: obj_class SearchPage
    CMS: attribute show_in_navigation (enum)
    CMS: attribute search_page_link (linklist)
    Misc: extends app/models/homepage.rb
    Misc: extends app/views/layouts/application.html.haml
    Misc: adds app/cells/search_cell.rb